==闻屁==
闻屁是指嗅闻[[人类|人类]]或其他[[动物|动物]]的屁的行为。中国媒体曾报道有闻屁师这一职业<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2012-11/28/c_124012844.htm|title=职业“闻屁师”很吃香：年薪30万不能吸烟和饮酒 - 新华时政 - 新华网|accessdate=2018-01-24|work=news.xinhuanet.com|archive-date=2013-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130413222213/http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2012-11/28/c_124012844.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

